<div class="credit">
<p data-aid="154070677" id="figure1_p1">Minerva Teichert (1888&#x2013;1976), <cite>Escape of King Limhi and His People</cite>, 1949&#x2013;1951, oil on masonite, 35&#xA0;7/8&#xA0;&#xD7;&#xA0;48 inches. Brigham Young University Museum of Art,&#xA0;1969.</p>
