</section>
<section>
<header>
<p class="scripture-title" data-aid="154070927" id="scripture_title5"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27?lang=eng&amp;id=p8-p24#p8">Mosiah 27:8&#x2013;24</a></p>
<h3 data-aid="154070931" id="title7"><span class="iconPointer-OKie_ icon-eLakR icon-ieVZ1" data-pointer-type="media" data-scroll-id="title7" title="Associated Content"><button aria-label="Associated Content" class="iconPointerButton-Z_d47"><svg class="sc-vl6hp0-0 iOmaky Icon-Sax6y" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation"> <path fill="currentColor" d="M21.523 8.984l.014 12.478H6.028L6.023 8.977l15.5.007zm-17-.772v14c0 .414.335.75.75.75h17a.75.75 0 00.75-.75v-14a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75h-17a.75.75 0 00-.75.75zm11.624 7.32c.242-.342.638-.334.88.01l2.853 4.041c.245.347.106.629-.33.629H8.089c-.418 0-.566-.286-.335-.634l3.99-6.018c.233-.35.606-.355.843.003l2.398 3.616 1.162-1.647zm2.428-2.32a1.5 1.5 0 100-3 1.5 1.5 0 000 3zM17.477 1.026a.75.75 0 01.885.434l.033.096 1.314 4.905h-1.547l-1.015-3.77L2.173 6.694l1.349 5.028v5.804L.526 6.344A.75.75 0 01.96 5.46l.096-.033 16.42-4.4zm-2.86 3.613a1.5 1.5 0 011.841 1.823h-2.906a1.5 1.5 0 011.065-1.823z"> </path></svg></button></span>God hears my prayers and will answer them according to His will and timing.</h3>
</header>
<p data-aid="154070933" id="p13">Maybe you&#x2019;ve been in Alma the Elder&#x2019;s situation with a family member who is making destructive choices. What do you find in <a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27?lang=eng&amp;id=p8-p24#p8">Mosiah 27:8&#x2013;24</a> that gives you hope? How might these verses influence your prayers on behalf of others?</p>
<figure class="teaching-method" id="figure6">
<p data-aid="154070938" id="figure6_p1">For more ideas, see this month&#x2019;s issues of the <cite><a class="cross-ref" href="/study/liahona/2024/05?lang=eng">Liahona</a></cite> and <cite><a class="cross-ref" href="/study/ftsoy/2024/05?lang=eng">For the Strength of Youth</a></cite> magazines.</p>
</figure>
</section>
</section>
<section>
<header>
<h2 data-aid="154070940" id="title8">Ideas for Teaching Children</h2>
</header>
<section>
<header>
<p class="scripture-title" data-aid="154070944" id="scripture_title6"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26?lang=eng&amp;id=p30-p31#p30">Mosiah 26:30&#x2013;31</a></p>
<h3 data-aid="154070949" id="title9"><span class="iconPointer-OKie_ icon-eLakR icon-ieVZ1" data-pointer-type="media" data-scroll-id="title9" title="Associated Content"><button aria-label="Associated Content" class="iconPointerButton-Z_d47"><svg class="sc-vl6hp0-0 iOmaky Icon-Sax6y" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation"> <path fill="currentColor" d="M21.523 8.984l.014 12.478H6.028L6.023 8.977l15.5.007zm-17-.772v14c0 .414.335.75.75.75h17a.75.75 0 00.75-.75v-14a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75h-17a.75.75 0 00-.75.75zm11.624 7.32c.242-.342.638-.334.88.01l2.853 4.041c.245.347.106.629-.33.629H8.089c-.418 0-.566-.286-.335-.634l3.99-6.018c.233-.35.606-.355.843.003l2.398 3.616 1.162-1.647zm2.428-2.32a1.5 1.5 0 100-3 1.5 1.5 0 000 3zM17.477 1.026a.75.75 0 01.885.434l.033.096 1.314 4.905h-1.547l-1.015-3.77L2.173 6.694l1.349 5.028v5.804L.526 6.344A.75.75 0 01.96 5.46l.096-.033 16.42-4.4zm-2.86 3.613a1.5 1.5 0 011.841 1.823h-2.906a1.5 1.5 0 011.065-1.823z"> </path></svg></button></span>The Lord wants me to forgive.</h3>
</header>
<ul class="bullet">
<li>
<p data-aid="154070954" id="p15">To help your children discover what the Lord taught Alma about forgiveness, you could invite them to read <a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26?lang=eng&amp;id=p29-p31#p29">Mosiah 26:29&#x2013;31</a> and count how many times the word &#x201C;forgive&#x201D; appears. What do these verses teach about forgiving others? (See also &#x201C;<a class="cross-ref" href="/study/manual/childrens-songbook/help-me-dear-father?lang=eng">Help Me, Dear Father</a>,&#x201D; <cite>Children&#x2019;s Songbook</cite>,&#xA0;99.)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p data-aid="154070958" id="p16">To emphasize the Savior&#x2019;s example of forgiveness, you could show a picture of Him on the cross and read together <a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/nt/luke/23?lang=eng&amp;id=p33-p34#p33">Luke 23:33&#x2013;34</a>. What did Jesus ask Heavenly Father to do for the people who put Him on the cross? After this discussion, your children could role-play forgiving each other.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p data-aid="154070961" id="p17">Sometimes it is difficult to forgive ourselves when we make mistakes. How can God&#x2019;s words to Alma help? Your children could pretend they are talking to someone who doesn&#x2019;t think God will ever forgive them. Invite your children to find something in <a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26?lang=eng&amp;id=p22-p23,29-p30#p22">Mosiah 26:22&#x2013;23, 29&#x2013;30</a> that might help that person.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section>
<header>
<p class="scripture-title" data-aid="154070965" id="scripture_title7"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27?lang=eng&amp;id=p8-p37#p8">Mosiah 27:8&#x2013;37</a></p>
<h3 data-aid="154070969" id="title10"><span class="iconPointer-OKie_ icon-eLakR icon-ieVZ1" data-pointer-type="media" data-scroll-id="title10" title="Associated Content"><button aria-label="Associated Content" class="iconPointerButton-Z_d47"><svg class="sc-vl6hp0-0 iOmaky Icon-Sax6y" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation"> <path fill="currentColor" d="M21.523 8.984l.014 12.478H6.028L6.023 8.977l15.5.007zm-17-.772v14c0 .414.335.75.75.75h17a.75.75 0 00.75-.75v-14a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75h-17a.75.75 0 00-.75.75zm11.624 7.32c.242-.342.638-.334.88.01l2.853 4.041c.245.347.106.629-.33.629H8.089c-.418 0-.566-.286-.335-.634l3.99-6.018c.233-.35.606-.355.843.003l2.398 3.616 1.162-1.647zm2.428-2.32a1.5 1.5 0 100-3 1.5 1.5 0 000 3zM17.477 1.026a.75.75 0 01.885.434l.033.096 1.314 4.905h-1.547l-1.015-3.77L2.173 6.694l1.349 5.028v5.804L.526 6.344A.75.75 0 01.96 5.46l.096-.033 16.42-4.4zm-2.86 3.613a1.5 1.5 0 011.841 1.823h-2.906a1.5 1.5 0 011.065-1.823z"> </path></svg></button></span>Jesus Christ helps me become more like Him.</h3>
</header>
<ul class="bullet">
<li>
<p data-aid="154070973" id="p18">The conversion of Alma the Younger and the sons of Mosiah could show your children that, with the Savior&#x2019;s power, anyone can change. You or your children could use the paintings in this outline, this week&#x2019;s activity page, and a few key scriptures from <a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27?lang=eng&amp;id=p8-p37#p8">Mosiah 27:8&#x2013;37</a> to tell the story (see also &#x201C;<span class="legacy-cross-ref" data-legacy-href="manual/book-of-mormon-stories-2024/22-alma-the-younger.html">Chapter&#xA0;18: Alma the Younger Repents</span>,&#x201D; in <cite>Book of Mormon Stories</cite>, 49&#x2013;52). Give special emphasis to <a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27?lang=eng&amp;id=p24#p24">verse&#xA0;24</a>, to teach that Alma repented and Jesus Christ helped him change. Let your children act out the story if they&#x2019;d like.</p>
<div class="sc-bvqtyr-0 duiKkI video-vMiKm video"><div class="sc-bvqtyr-1 inwLwu"><div class="sc-bvqtyr-2 hQntbb"><img alt="" class="posterFallback-wNf54" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 320px, 640px" srcset="
            https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/imgs/https%3A%2F%2Fassets.churchofjesuschrist.org%2F9a%2Fc1%2F9ac1799ad8a8be2edb8a44beb6316d5bb4053129%2F9ac1799ad8a8be2edb8a44beb6316d5bb4053129.jpeg/full/!320,/0/default 320w,
            https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/imgs/https%3A%2F%2Fassets.churchofjesuschrist.org%2F9a%2Fc1%2F9ac1799ad8a8be2edb8a44beb6316d5bb4053129%2F9ac1799ad8a8be2edb8a44beb6316d5bb4053129.jpeg/full/!640,/0/default 640w
        " src="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/imgs/${posterReference}/full/!250,/0/default"/><button aria-label="
                Play - Alma the Younger
            " class="sc-1g7hsbc-0 bCKkuP sc-bvqtyr-3 zrTrR" type="button"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" class="sc-1kfl9f7-0 hvmWVP"> <path fill="currentColor" d="M7.13 20.833c-.625.386-1.13.08-1.13-.678V3.845c0-.758.505-1.064 1.13-.678l13.401 8.155c.625.372.625.984 0 1.356l-13.4 8.155z"> </path></svg></button></div><div/></div></div>
</li>
</ul>
</section>
<figure class="image no-print" id="figure3">
<a class="enlarge" to="[object Object]" href="https://assets.churchofjesuschrist.org/d5/34/d534e672da22b644618b8e1f00562e357454d8df/alma_younger_mosiah_walter_rane.jpeg">
<div class="imageWrapper-wTPPD"><figure class="loadImageItem-u5D4D" title="Alma the Younger being carried to his father&#x2019;s house"><img width="320" height="168" alt=""/><div class="container-W4jed"><div class="innerFlex-R9N_u"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" class="sc-1d18oav-0 bYvpFK"> <path fill="currentColor" d="M20 4.75L19.25 4v16l.75-.75H4l.75.75V4L4 4.75h16zM3.25 4v16c0 .414.336.75.75.75h16a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75V4a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75H4a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75zm11.07 8.888c.23-.357.606-.353.828-.008l2.887 4.482c.227.352.06.638-.357.638H6.326c-.421 0-.581-.3-.37-.648l4.006-6.622c.217-.358.567-.359.793.014l2.396 3.96 1.17-1.816zm1.59-2.735c1.14 0 2.066-.907 2.066-2.026 0-1.12-.926-2.027-2.067-2.027s-2.066.907-2.066 2.027c0 1.119.925 2.026 2.066 2.026z"> </path></svg><div class="sc-1szn76m-0 gUZQGm i18nString-raclU">Image</div><div class="sc-1szn76m-0 gUZQGm title-RrK9J">Alma the Younger being carried to his father&#x2019;s house</div></div></div></figure></div>
